articles.title: About this site
articles.description: Some additional details about the website
articles.contents:
About me
I am Ajay Malik, an incoming senior at William Fremd High School. I like to ride my bike during the summer, and code in R and Python.
About the project
This project is titled High School Performance and Future Salary, by College, and this project analyzes the correlation between high performance in high school and predicted future salary.
Goals
To learn how to make neat websites using Distill
Titling is a bit weird but I will figure it out

To create easy-to-understand visualizations that are available on the web
“This is data science”
Preceptor

“Kane’s Free High School Data Science Bootcamp”

articles.title: High School Performance and Future Salary, by College
articles.description: This project analyzes a small subset of colleges in the US in order to establish a correlation between the performance of the undergraduates of these colleges in high school, and their mid-career median salary. As you can see, the trend is mostly positive.
